kbzHY"><h4 class=3D"FAQ_faq__section-title__hFcCV">What is px unit? (Pixels=
)</h4><p class=3D"FAQ_faq__section-text__8mXlS">Pixel unit is the theorical=
 smallest dot displayed on a computer screen.
